org.sql: SELECT queries.* FROM queries LEFT OUTER JOIN projects ON queries.project_id = projects.id WHERE queries.type IN ('IssueQuery') AND (queries.project_id IS NULL OR projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'issue_tracking') IS NOT NULL AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (3, 12))) AND (queries.visibility = 2 OR queries.user_id = 3) AND queries.id = "$1" LIMIT 1
